### Voting system related console commands

## 'protovote' command

cmd-protovote-desc = Creates a custom prototye vote
cmd-protovote-help = Usage: protovote <title> <option1> <option2> [option3...]
cmd-protovote-on-finished-tie = The vote '{$title}' has finished: tie between {$ties}!
cmd-protovote-on-finished-win = The vote '{$title}' has finished: {$winner} wins!
cmd-protovote-arg-title = <title>
cmd-protovote-arg-option-n = <option{ $n }>
cmd-protovote-error-no-prototype = Prototype not found: {$proto}
